## Three subsystems

| Subsystem | Path | Deploy |
|-----------|------|--------|
| Portfolio V3 | `src/v3/` | GitHub Pages (`docs/`) |
| Laravel API (forms/analytics) | `api-carlxaeron/` | Namecheap Stellar → `https://api.carlmanuel.com` (hosting-ssh) |
| Firebase (Analytics + leftover handlers) | `functions/` / `src/config.js` | Assistant + weekly on hosting-php; license deleted |
