| Client quotation sites | `client-sites/` | Netlify per folder · [catalog](client-sites/README.md) |

## Portfolio modes

- **Default:** 7-section slide deck (`home` … `quote`)
- **Preview:** `?preview={slug}` (e.g. `?preview=jk-construction`) → device showcase (desktop 1280×800 + mobile 390×844 iframes, scaled to mockups). Legacy `*.netlify.app` hostnames still resolve and normalize to slug.
- **Client demos:** embed-only on Netlify — direct URL blocked; view via portfolio preview only · [site catalog](client-sites/README.md)
- **Client stack:** Tailwind CDN + `site.js` (nav/accordions/reveal) + **Motion** (`hero-motion.js`) + **Three.js** (`hero-three.js` ambient canvas) on the first-section hero
- **Outreach:** each `client-sites/{slug}/` includes draft email, SMS, and messenger quotations

`home` → `about` → `skills` → `experience` → `projects` → `contact` → `quote`

Config: `src/v3/containers/Portfolio/Portfolio.js` · Content: `src/external-config.js` · Preview: `src/v3/config/previewWhitelist.js`

