## Hard rules

- Do **not** edit plan files in `.cursor/plans/`
- Do **not** commit `job-applications/`, `exports/`, `.env` secrets
- **Test before deploy:** hosting-php / Laravel / Firebase — see `.cursor/rules/test-before-deploy.mdc`
- **Proactively keep `.cursor/skills/`, `.cursor/rules/`, and `AGENTS.md` accurate** when workflows change or docs are stale — user need not ask; keep diffs small and helpful (see AGENTS.md “Keep agent docs current”)
- Side project copy: **short**; client projects: **long** case studies
- Never mention **Tahanan** in OnlineJobs `submission.txt`
